            "author": "Ashley Post",
            "location": "Houston, TX"
          }
        },
        "r7": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "This place is THE best! My tans always come out incredibly even (yes, including hands + feet), have the perfect color/undertone every time, and fade nicely. Every artist has made me extremely comfortable.",
            "author": "Hali Crawford",
            "location": "Austin, TX"
          }
        },
        "r8": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Had a great experience at Hush Hush Tan! Ashly helped me at the front & Jacinda sprayed me :) Very easy to book online, super cute inside \u2014 my tan looked perfect for my friends wedding.",
            "author": "Calla Taylor",
            "location": "Dallas, TX"
          }
        },
        "r9": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "I had the absolute best experience with Ale at Hush Hush Tan! From the moment I walked in, she made me feel so comfortable and welcomed. She is incredibly knowledgeable, professional, and truly pays attention to detail.",
            "author": "Gracie Solano",
            "location": "Houston, TX"
          }
        },
        "r10": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Greeted by Chloe, who was incredibly kind and helpful during my first tan at Hush Hush. I was sprayed by Tarin, who had amazing attention to detail and made the entire experience feel comfortable and never awkward.",
            "author": "Emma Kenny",
            "location": "Austin, TX"
          }
        },
        "r11": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Tried HushHush today after coming from another local tanning salon that does airbrush, and what a world of difference. Amanda was very thorough and detailed, and the overall experience was great.",
